query:
SELECT 
  id,
  txid,
  customerId,
  amount,
  status,
  createdAt,
  paidAt,
  TIMESTAMPDIFF(MINUTE, createdAt, NOW()) as minutosDesdeC riacao
FROM pix_transactions
WHERE customerId = 480001 AND amount = 120
ORDER BY createdAt DESC
LIMIT 1
